            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".NEUTRON FLUX WAS MEASURED WITH A STILBEN",
                " PROTON RECOIL SPECTROMETER. BECAUSE OF THE Q-VALUE OF",
                " -18.72 MEV FOR THE C-12(N,2N)C-11 REACTION, LOW ENERGY",
                " NEUTRONS FROM TRITIUM BACK UP AND INDUCED REACTIONS",
